"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?6/49/6936?source=related_link\">",
"      Subdural hematoma in adults: Etiology, clinical features, and diagnosis",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?6/54/7014?source=related_link\">",
